data.description: Top quality workmanship in this newer home not far out of town. Huge, nearly two acre lot for your privacy. Entertain on the multi-level back patio and deck with Sunesta retractable awning for those lovely summer nights. The yard stay gorgeous with an in ground sprinkler system and beautiful Landscaping. There is a large Bonus Room that can flex from office to bedroom space according to your need. Also, there is a potential bedroom area in the lower level that can be finished replete with egress. Ample three car garage for toy storage or workshop. You will love the highly functional kitchen with topnotch appliances still under transferable warranty until October 2024 and granite countertops. Lower level Finished Basement Theatre has all the finish touches of cozy comfort for the winter evenings! This home is a highly functional work of art and beauty! Current financing may allow assumable loan for qualified buyers. Home Warranty provided by listing broker.
